# Strapi Components

## What are Components?

Components in Strapi are reusable content structures that can be used across different content types. They help in creating modular and reusable content blocks.

## Available Components

### Footer Components

The footer components provide structure for the site's footer:

- @Contact Us - Contact information component
  - Social media links
  - Phone number
  - Messaging contacts

- @Footer Link Item - Individual footer link
  - Title
  - URL

- @Footer Section - Section in the footer
  - Header
  - Links (multiple Footer Link Items)

## Using Components in Content Types

Components are used in content types to create reusable structures:

```typescript
// Example of using Footer components in schema.json
{
  "kind": "singleType",
  "collectionName": "footers",
  "info": {
    "singularName": "footer",
    "pluralName": "footers",
    "displayName": "Footer"
  },
  "attributes": {
    "CopyrightText": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "Sections": {
      "type": "component",
      "repeatable": true,
      "component": "footer.footer-section"
    },
    "ContactInfo": {
      "type": "component",
      "repeatable": false,
      "component": "footer.contact-us"
    }
  }
}
```

## TypeScript Interface for Components

Generated TypeScript interfaces are available for all components:

```typescript
// From types/generated/components.d.ts
export interface FooterContactUs extends Schema.Component {
  collectionName: 'components_footer_contactuses';
  info: {
    displayName: 'ContactUs';
    icon: 'apps';
  };
  attributes: {
    Instagram: Attribute.String;
    Phone: Attribute.String & Attribute.Required;
    Telegram: Attribute.String;
    Whatsapp: Attribute.String;
  };
}

export interface FooterFooterLinkItem extends Schema.Component {
  collectionName: 'components_footer_footer_link_items';
  info: {
    displayName: 'FooterLinkItem';
    icon: 'bulletList';
  };
  attributes: {
    Title: Attribute.String & Attribute.Required;
    URL: Attribute.Text & Attribute.Required;
  };
}

export interface FooterFooterSection extends Schema.Component {
  collectionName: 'components_footer_footer_sections';
  info: {
    displayName: 'FooterSection';
    icon: 'connector';
  };
  attributes: {
    Header: Attribute.String;
    Links: Attribute.Component<'footer.footer-link-item', true>;
  };
}
```

